Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Raise the Windows GPU TDR timeout to 60s so RenderDoc can capture Elden Ring without DXGI_DEVICE_REMOVED
; (RenderDoc's overhead during ER's title load overruns the default 2s GPU-op timeout -> TDR). Only affects
; GPU-hang recovery; normal gameplay is unchanged. Double-click + confirm UAC, or `reg import` elevated,
; then REBOOT. Revert: set both back to dword:00000002 (or delete the values). bd RENDERDOC-deviceremoved-is-TDR.
[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\GraphicsDrivers]
"TdrDelay"=dword:0000003c
"TdrDdiDelay"=dword:0000003c
